Achievements.Description: Unlock 30 Character skills from the Skill Tree.

Achievements.Name: Seasoned Traveler
Achievements.Description: Ride a mount and a motorcycle, drive a car, and pilot a flying vehicle.

Achievements.Description: Link 5 Toy Boxes together with Toy Box Doors.

Achievements.Name: Toy Box Maker
Achievements.Description: Publish your own Toy Box Game.

Achievements.Description: Purchase a full page of toys from the Toy Store.

Achievements.Description: Play a Toy Box Game with 2 players.

Achievements.Description: Collect 50 pieces of equipment for your sidekicks.

Achievements.Name: Trap Master
Achievements.Description: Place 50 traps in Assault on Asgard or Stitch's Tropical Rescue.

Achievements.Description: Purchase 25 INterior decorations from the Toy Store.

Achievements.Name: Master Decorator
Achievements.Description: Purchase 50 INterior decorations from the Toy Store.
